Title: The 'C' Word
Plot: Being the boss isn't all it's cracked up to be when Liz overhears the writers discussing her management style and Jack tries to impress CEO Don Geiss (Rip Torn) at a charity golf tournament by bringing Tracy along.
GuestStars: Darlene J. Camille, Paul Doherty, Tamara Fay, Rachel Hamilton, Kevin Miller, Charlene Yi, Teresa Yenque, Tom Treadwell, Sam Kitchin, Justin Badger
